{"type":"message","id":"02f2b80f","parentId":"a6821d69","timestamp":"2026-03-18T17:04:32.457Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are already 34 knowledge files in the directory. Let me create a new knowledge article based on the perception results and my understanding of desktop aesthetics and optimization. Then I'll update the memory file.Let me write a new knowledge piece about Windows desktop optimization and aesthetics.","thinkingSignature":"d8c7cf044fc5c85aa0c8238a6e4c9698f06c4a2263ada8955e614d209451097f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n9ap1ida2bje_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 桌面美学与系统优化实践\n\n## 核心要点\n\n### 1. 内存优化\n- 当前内存使用率 85.7%，建议清理后台进程\n- 定期使用任务管理器结束不用的应用\n\n### 2. 文件整理\n- Downloads 文件夹容易堆积文件\n- 建议按月份/类型分类整理\n\n### 3. 桌面美学\n- 壁纸选择：海洋/自然主题最受欢迎\n- 保持桌面简洁：只放常用图标\n- 定期更换壁纸保持新鲜感\n\n## 可行动指引\n\n| 任务 | 频率 | 工具 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 内存清理 | 每天 | 任务管理器 |\n| Downloads整理 | 每周 | 文件资源管理器 |\n| 壁纸更换 | 每月 | OpenClaw |\n| 桌面整理 | 每周 | 手动/脚本 |\n\n## 2026 趋势\n\n1. **动态壁纸** - 视频/交互式壁纸流行\n2. **主题系统** - 统一主题色\n3. **极简主义** - 减少视觉噪音\n4. **自然元素** - 植物/海洋/天空\n","file_path":"C:/Users/16343/.openclaw/agents/xiao-yi/workspace/knowledge/35-桌面美学与系统优化.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":2692,"output":360,"cacheRead":36266,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39318,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773853447271}}
